text: Julie Lengweiler (born 6 November 1998) is a Swiss volleyball player. She is a member of the Women's National Team. She participated at the 2016 FIVB Volleyball Women's Club World Championship, and 2017 Montreux Volley Masters. == Clubs == * Volero Zürich (2017–) == References == == External links == * FIVB Profile * CEV profile Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss women's volleyball players Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
